@node "Features" "Features"


                        @{b}Features of MEM Alert@{ub}


     * 2MB - 20MB memory settings (in 2mb steps)

     * 5MB - 100MB memory settings (in special version)

     * Alert on FAST or TOTAL memory

     * MEM Alert is small (about 21k including sample!!!!)

     * MEMTYPE Tooltype to set the either Total or Fast mem mode

     * MEMSIZE Tooltype to set the initial position of the slider

     * MEM Alert works with all programs.  (I think...!)


                     What more could you want......?

          (don't tell me, I already have a giant TO-DO list.!)


     @{"ReturnÝtoÝMainÝMenu" link "Main" 0}
@endnode

